OL,3,CShoplifter sets store on fire after
OL,4,Cbeing confronted for stealing alcohol
OL,6,FA man has been given a three year
OL,7,Fprison sentence for setting fire to a
OL,8,Fshop in Folkestone that he'd tried to
OL,9,Fsteal from.
OL,11,FShaun Brocklehurst, 42, was stopped by
OL,12,Fa man in a grocery store on Cheriton
OL,13,FHigh Street and was found with alcohol
OL,14,Fin his bag that he was attempting to
OL,15,Fsteal.
OL,17,FAn altercation followed, in which
OL,18,FBrocklehurst punched and kicked the
OL,19,Fman before leaving the premises.
