OL,3,CShoplifter sets store on fire after
OL,4,Cbeing confronted for stealing alcohol
OL,6,FAround half an hour later,
OL,7,FBrocklehurst returned with a small
OL,8,Ffuel can and poured a flammable liquid
OL,9,Fover the front of the shop and
OL,10,Figniting it, leading to a rush of
OL,11,Fflames.
OL,13,FHe then left the scene.
OL,15,FThe fire was extinguished quickly by a
OL,16,Fmember of the public and no injuries
OL,17,Fwere reported.
