OL,3,CShoplifter sets store on fire after
OL,4,Cbeing confronted for stealing alcohol
OL,6,FAn investigation by East Kent CID led
OL,7,Fto the arrest of Brocklehurst, of
OL,8,FPhillip Road, Folkestone, who was
OL,9,Fcharged with attempted robbery and
OL,10,Farson with recklessness as to whether
OL,11,Flife was endangered.
OL,13,FAfter pleading guilty, Brocklehurst
OL,14,Fwas sentenced at Canterbury Crown
OL,15,FCourt to three years' imprisonment.
