OL,3,CShoplifter sets store on fire after
OL,4,Cbeing confronted for stealing alcohol
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Joshua Wratten of
OL,7,FEast Kent CID, said: "Brocklehurst's
OL,8,Factions were completely reckless -
OL,9,Fendangering public safety with no
OL,10,Fregard for the consequences, which
OL,11,Fcould have been devastating.
OL,13,F"It is merciful that nobody was hurt
OL,14,Fas a result of his behaviour that day.
OL,16,F"I am pleased that a custodial
OL,17,Fsentence has been imposed, reflecting
OL,18,Fthe gravity of the case and would hope
OL,19,Fit serves as a reminder that this kind
OL,20,Fof behaviour in our communities will
OL,21,Fnot be tolerated."
